snippet: Lt. Gov. Jennifer Carroll’s ties to Gov. Rick Scott were seen as strained well before news broke that she had been caught up in a criminal investigation.
abstract: Former Florida Lt Gov Jennifer Carroll's ties to Gov Rick Scott were seen as strained well before news broke that she was caught up in criminal investigation, which prompted her resignation.

byline.original: By CHRISTINE JORDAN SEXTON and LIZETTE ALVAREZ
byline.contributor: Christine Jordan Sexton reported from Tallahassee, and Lizette Alvarez from Miami.

lead_paragraph: Lt. Gov. Jennifer Carroll’s ties to Gov. Rick Scott were seen as strained well before news broke that she had been caught up in a criminal investigation.

headline.seo: Jennifer Carroll Resignation Preceded by Tensions with Rick Scott
headline.main: In Florida, a Political Marriage Soured Before a Top Official Stepped Down
headline.print_headline: In Florida, a Political Marriage Soured Before a Top Official Stepped Down
